item.title: Very happy to present @brantcooper at #swbru
item.description: You guys missed a great talk. In 15 minutes Brant was able to motivate and help the participants more than some business courses can do in a semester. Inspiring, practical and funny. The best way to kickstart Startup Weekend Brussels, live from sunny San Diego.
